{'id': 21407215, 'body': 'So sorry for the trouble you've experienced! Please try leaving the app open on the loading screen, as this should allow the app to fully load. Upon subsequent app launches, the app should then load normally without any delay on the "take a deep breath" screen. If you are experiencing issues on an older version of the iOS app, please update to the latest version, then follow the steps above if you experience any loading issues.', 'modified': '2021-03-02T20:32:07Z'}{'id': 25648053, 'body': 'Thanks for the wonderful review! And, fear not, Sleep Check-ins are still available ;) 

On your Calm app's home screen, scroll down to the "Quick & Easy" section. Then, scroll through the options to the right until you find "How did you sleep?"

If you have any further trouble getting to your Sleep Check-ins, please reach out to our support team at www.calm.com/contact - they'd be happy to help you out!', 'modified': '2021-10-12T23:44:15Z'}
